data.name: descriptionTextBox.Text
data.value: Adjust your mouse's minimum double-click speed for each mouse button separately. In the logs, you see the elapsed time between clicks and any double-clicks that were ignored. See how long your double-clicks take and compare it to the faulty ones generated by your mouse. Fine-tune the minimum speed to include the faulty clicks while staying below your normal speed. Test your mouse's behavior with the current settings with the test text (single click, double-click, select text).
